Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:48.10,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3a&H5F&\pos(465.708,336)}{\fad(871,1052)}Dew frost
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The conference members are basically selected after we do a strict examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There really aren't any suspicious people, so to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or any people with problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there are any conflicts between two members,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we'll take responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.76,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,It was a job I just chose to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.81,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,because employment opportunities were limited for a third-class university graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:21.51,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Or so I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:27.89,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Or I was trying to make myself think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:34.76,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,In truth, I wanted to experience people's happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:37.69,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I wanted to experience people's sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:43.92,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I wanted to place myself somewhere where people encounter and separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:55.50,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,If I kept doing that, I thought I'd be able to do the same someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From now on, I want you to help me with the house chores more often than before, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel kind of bad doing this to you since there's such a large age difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You don't seem too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're finally going to be a big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't it almost time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a big brother now, aren't you, Ko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! We did it, Koshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, it's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:03.98,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,It was a kind of a happy, yet scary, feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:10.64,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,But that was the only time I had that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, my, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh... Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't cry, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't bullying her while we're out, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka seems to be afraid of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you come to the other room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that we're quarreling with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or we got into a big fight or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought we should live separately before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're sorry that we have to make you go through some sad times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're really sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though we'll be living apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it doesn't mean I'll stop being your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or that she's no longer your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're still family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:43.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:55.56,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I thought divorces weren't such peaceful things in my mind as a child, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:08:03.18,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I could tell that mom and dad were trying to separate peacefully for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro, keep an eye on the house for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't look so sulky forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be more honest with yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:42.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can come any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, you've been going home early lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must want to see Nanoka-san as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so envious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way. He's not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:35.82,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I love you, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:54.51,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Why is it that I even headed there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.46,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Without even understanding it myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:11.70,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I was walking in the town that she grew up in without me knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you finally came to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I'd know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you, Koshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you would've forgotten my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you forget my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? Even if we haven't seen each other for years, that's how it is between a parent and child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:10:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just suddenly came. There must be some reason, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No reason. I just felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From when she was a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She just loves bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She really is your younger sister, that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You exchanged dolls, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka was talking about it so happily when she came back during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you send her over to our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you took her with you when you got divorced,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why would you suddenly bring her back to dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because she got into a high school near your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd feel bad if she had to commute two hours each way every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? did you come all the way over just to sulk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many years has it been since I last cut your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't let me cut it much after you became a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you getting all worked up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She isn't bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying, Onii-chan, Onii-chan, Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.15,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Onii-chan is like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.99,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I want to meet him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:40.07,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he'll help me with studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.20,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.62,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,He will help you, I'm sure, with your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:49.45,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:14:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably really wanted to live with you guys... or just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So take good care of her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zenzou-san is no good when you really need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You'd better make sure you take care of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a big brother, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What would you do if I made her unhappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I somehow made her unhappy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If such a thing happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't let you get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weird kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still don't seem to be very honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It means you haven't grown up at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the most difficult phase
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,at that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay a little longer, since its been a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have work tomorrow too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to eat properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yes. Nanoka's flavoring is usually a little too strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so tell her to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And don't give her too much allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't give her any even if she begged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And tell her not to stay up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it already. I'll be late for my train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Koshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get along with her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm... home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not going to cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you go today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should've taken me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:46.68,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with being Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.77,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with just being close to each other as siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:54.10,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,If that's the role that I was given,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.24,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'll do what I must.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:20:59.68,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to get up early tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you too, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take a smoke and then go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:42.30,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,So don't say that you love me.
